headline: Q3 2025 Insurance Labor Market Study Results to be Highlighted in Webinar
summary: CHICAGO, July 29, 2025--The results of the Q3 2025 U.S. Insurance Labor Market Study will be revealed in a webinar presentation at 1 p.m. CDT on August 7, 2025.

headline: Companies Struggle to Meet Rising Demand for Personalized Benefits, Aon Survey Finds
summary: Aon plc (NYSE: AON), a leading global professional services firm, today released its 2025 Global Benefits Trends Study, which finds that multinational companies are under mounting pressure to offer personalized, inclusive benefits – yet most lack the governance, tools or frameworks to deliver at scale. The study, based on responses from more than 500 global benefits professionals across 45 countries and 16 industries, reveals that only 14 percent of multinationals have global guidelines in place
